22%3Erecent%20turmoil%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shares%20of%20Nvidia%20are%20still%20up%20by%20more%20than%20100%25%20from%20this%20time%20in%202023%20and%20by%20more%20than%202%2C000%25%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20quarterly%20earnings%20reports%20have%20turned%20into%20a%20referendum%20on%20the%20future%20of%20the%20whole%20stock%20market%20and%20even%20the%20US%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20a%20highly%20anticipated%20financial%20event%20like%20the%20jobs%20report%20or%20an%20inflation%20print.%20Nvidia's%20most%20recent%20earnings%20report%20prompted%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-earnings-watch-party-bar-nyc-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunofficial%20watch%20party%20in%20New%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20CEO%2C%20Jensen%20Huang%2C%20has%20achieved%20rock-star%20status%2C%20and%20his%20leather-jacket%20aesthetic%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-wardrobe-black-leather-jackets-signature-look-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20subject%20of%20endless%20media%20fodder%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20the%20spring%2C%20the%20company%20hosted%20a%20four-day%20conference%20that%20observers%20informally%20dubbed%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-humanoid-robots-jensen-huang-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20Woodstock%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20see%20these%20types%20of%20disruptive%20technologies%20or%20companies%20out%20there%2C%20there%20are%20just%20both%20institutional%20and%20retail%20investors%20out%20there%20that%20really%20kind%20of%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20these%20stories%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Angelo%20Zino%2C%20a%20senior%20vice%20president%20at%20CFRA%20Research%20who%20covers%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20you're%20not%20trying%20to%20pay%20attention%2C%20you%20sort%20of%20can't%20escape%20Nvidia%20mania.%20It's%20a%20significant%20chunk%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%20Its%20moves%20are%20all%20over%20the%20news.%20Hell%2C%20even%20the%20CNBC%20host%20Jim%20Cramer%20named%20his%20dog%20after%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20people%20were%20going%20to%20be%20going%20crazy%20about%20a%20stock%2C%20wouldn't%20it%20be%20this%20one%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Josh%20Brown%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Ritholtz%20Wealth%20Management%20and%20a%20market%20commentator.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20wouldn't%20people%20be%20as%20enthusiastic%20as%20they%20are%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20Nvidia%20is%20a%20big%20deal%2C%20the%20fanfare%20is%20a%20little%20weird.%20It's%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20weird%20as%20that%20one%20coworker%20who%20talks%20about%20their%20cat%20too%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Emuch%20or%20the%20friend%20who%20seems%20to%20still%20know%20an%20awful%20lot%20about%20their%20ex%20from%20a%20decade%20ago.%20It's%20giving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwelcome-to-elon-musks-fan-club-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20fanboys%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-made-nfl-more-popular-in-america-us-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENFL%20Swifties%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-khive-kamala-harris-fiercely-loyal-group-online-fans-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20KHive%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20Kamala%20Harris%20was%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Democratic%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20saying%20Nvidia%20is%20a%20cult%2C%20but%20the%20whole%20thing%20is%20a%20bit%20culty.%20A%20lot%20of%20investors%20could%20probably%20stand%20to%20calm%20down.%20Fandom%20is%20always%20a%20little%20strange%2C%20but%20this%20kind%20of%20attachment%20is%20even%20more%20peculiar%20when%20it's%20to%20a%20stock%20%E2%80%94%20as%20any%20half-decent%20financial%20advisor%20can%20tell%20you%2C%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20ways%20to%20get%20ahead%20in%20investing%20is%20to%20keep%20your%20emotions%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20reached%20out%20to%20Serious%20Wall%20Street%20People%20and%20random%20retail%20investors%20I%20found%20on%20the%20internet%20to%20talk%20about%20what%20they%20make%20of%20all%20the%20Nvidia%20hullabaloo.%20What%20was%20striking%20was%20how%20alike%20many%20of%20them%20sounded.%20Dan%20Ives%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Wedbush%20Securities%2C%20compared%20Nvidia%20to%20%26quot%3BLebron%20in%20high%20school%26quot%3B%20and%20described%20Huang%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bgodfather%20of%20AI%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bgrand-master%20chess%20player.%26quot%3B%20Both%20he%20and%20Daniel%20Williams%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20day%20trader%20from%20New%20York%2C%20emphasized%20their%20belief%20that%20the%20company%20is%20leading%20the%20fourth%20industrial%20revolution.%20%26quot%3BNvidia%20is%20the%20quarterback%2C%26quot%3B%20Williams%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20market%20often%20framed%20as%20the%20retail%20day-trading%20Davids%20versus%20the%20institutional%20Wall%20Street%20Goliaths%2C%20Nvidia%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20one%20thing%20that%20can%20get%20David%20and%20Goliath%20to%20hold%20hands%20and%20skip%20through%20a%20meadow.%20Everybody%20likes%20it%20when%20the%20number%20goes%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20academic%20research%20about%20why%20retail%20investors%20buy%20stock%2C%20and%20the%20No.%201%20attention%20grabber%20is%20big%20returns%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Christopher%20Schwarz%2C%20a%20finance%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%20Irvine's%20Paul%20Merage%20School%20of%20Business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20a%20successful%20business%20that's%20achieved%20meme%20status.%20It%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20and%20if%20you%20think%20this%20whole%20AI%20thing%20is%20going%20to%20work%20out%20and%20Nvidia's%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20keep%20competitors%20at%20bay%2C%20there's%20no%20reason%20to%20think%20it's%20anything%20short%20of%20a%20great%20investment.%20It's%20also%20volatile%2C%20and%20that%20roller-coaster%20thrill%20can%20add%20to%20the%20appeal%20for%20some%20traders.%20As%20Axios'%20Felix%20Salmon%20recently%20pointed%20out%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2024%2F09%2F03%2Fnvidias-stock-price-gamblers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20can%20be%20an%20avenue%20for%20investors%20to%20scratch%20that%20gambling%20itch%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJack%2C%20a%20moderator%20of%20a%20subreddit%20dedicated%20to%20Nvidia's%20stock%2C%20finds%20some%20of%20the%20memes%20around%20Nvidia%20irksome.%20He%20became%20one%20of%20the%20forum's%20referees%20after%20complaining%20that%20%26quot%3Bmindless%20nonsense%26quot%3B%20there%20diluted%20its%20value%20as%20an%20information%20source.%20On%20big%20days%20for%20Nvidia%2C%20like%20when%20it%20releases%20its%20earnings%20reports%2C%20he%20focuses%20on%20keeping%20the%20subreddit%20from%20catching%20fire%20and%20leaves%20his%20holdings%20alone.%20Jack%2C%20a%20psychology%20student%20in%20Maine%20who%20asked%20to%20have%20his%20last%20name%20withheld%20to%20protect%20his%20privacy%2C%20is%20a%20pretty%20straightforward%20investor%2C%20but%20he's%20also%2023%2C%20and%20he%20came%20up%20in%20the%20era%20of%20Wall%20Street%20Bets%20and%20GameStop.%20He%20knows%20that%2C%20businesswise%2C%20Nvidia%20is%20vastly%20different%20from%20GameStop%20%E2%80%94%20an%20advanced%20tech%20company%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20a%20monumental%20computing%20shift%20is%20not%20the%20same%20as%20a%20video-game%20retailer%20in%20structural%20decline.%20But%20given%20the%20sheer%20number%20of%20wild%20bets%20made%20on%20the%20chipmaker%2C%20mostly%20through%20options%20trading%2C%20Jack%20can't%20help%20make%20the%20comparison%2C%20at%20least%20meme-wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20%26quot%3Bisn't%2C%20like%2C%20a%20joke%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20actually%20seriously%20one%20of%20the%20most%20innovative%20and%20quickly%20growing%20companies%20that%20the%20world%20has%20ever%20seen.%20And%20so%20I%20think%20that%20people%20are%20kind%20of%20treating%20it%20as%20if%20it's%20GameStop%2C%20where%20it%20has%20this%20incredible%20jump%2C%20and%20they're%20like%2C%20'Oh%20my%20God%2C%20what%20is%20this%20going%20to%20turn%20into%3F'%20So%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20fear%20around%20it%2C%20but%20in%20reality%2C%20the%20numbers%20go%20to%20show%20that%20it's%20quite%20sustainable%2C%20actually.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fervor%20Nvidia%20is%20generating%20isn't%20exactly%20like%20interest%20in%20other%20companies%20or%20investments%2C%20past%20and%20present.%20Some%20of%20this%20feels%20Tesla-esque%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20of%20investors%20who%20are%20dedicated%20to%20a%20company%20and%20CEO%20and%20who%20sometimes%20feverishly%20fight%20off%20detractors.%20Or%20it%20can%20look%20like%20Apple%2C%20beloved%20by%20many%20investors%20and%20actual%20customers%2C%20though%20Nvidia's%20recent%20rise%20has%20been%20faster%20and%20come%20later%20in%20the%20company's%20life.%20Some%20of%20the%20speculation%20around%20Nvidia%20seems%20a%20little%20crypto-y%2C%20as%20does%20the%20drumbeat%20of%20retail%20interest%20in%20it.%20If%20you%20squint%2C%20you%20can%20see%20a%20resemblance%20to%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20and%20Warren%20Buffett%2C%20who%20together%20draw%20thousands%20of%20people%20to%20Omaha%2C%20Nebraska%2C%20every%20year%20and%20garner%20headlines%20every%20time%20they%20release%20financial%20results%20or%20holdings%20%E2%80%94%20or%20Buffett%20just%20says%20something.%20There's%20also%20a%20not-so-rosy%20comparison%20to%20Nvidia%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-history-demise-cisco-sun-microsystems-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECisco%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20'90s%20tech%20darling%20that%20never%20recovered%20from%20the%20dot-com%20bubble's%20burst.%20Huang%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Da072bbf65eb3f1130fe3f2aad2d227bd8275bd3c00ca803fe01758def1b11cea%26postID%3D66d70d2c71b62b11ae91f987%26postSlug%3Dnvidia-stock-price-earnings-party-investors-cult-investing-memes-2024-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theinformation.com%252Farticles%252Fno-longer-the-underdog-nvidia-now-has-a-lot-to-prove%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20it%20and%20wants%20to%20make%20sure%20his%20company%20doesn't%20meet%20the%20same%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCisco%20is%20a%20great%20analogy%20to%20what's%20going%20on%20where%20just%20people%20just%20fawn%20over%20these%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Schwarz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20argued%20that%20there%20really%20isn't%20anything%20you%20can%20compare%20Nvidia%20to%20at%20the%20moment.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20there%20is%20any%20analogue%20throughout%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20much%20miraculous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETed%20Mortonson%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20at%20the%20investment%20firm%20Baird%2C%20also%20emphasized%20the%20unprecedented%20nature%20of%20it%20all%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20Nvidia%20is%20bringing%20in.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20defied%20the%20law%20of%20gravity%20from%20a%20model%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20one%20of%20these%20companies%20you%20see%20in%20every%20couple%20of%20decades.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20not%20a%20stock%20analyst%2C%20nor%20do%20I%20pretend%20to%20be%20one.%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20where%20Nvidia%20is%20headed%20in%20the%20next%20six%20months%20or%20two%20years%20or%20five%20years%2C%20nor%20can%20I%20predict%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-exaggeration-openai-nvidia-microsoft-chatgpt-jobs-investors-markets-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20will%20%E2%80%94%20or%20won't%20%E2%80%94%20happen%20with%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20Nvidia%2C%20though%2C%20that%20doesn't%20make%20me%20an%20outlier.%20Everyone%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20Reddit%20options%20traders%20betting%20each%20week%20on%20whether%20the%20stock%20will%20go%20up%20or%20down%20to%20the%20TV%20analysts%20cooly%20declaring%20that%20the%20robots%20will%20take%20everyone's%20jobs%20in%20five%20years%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20guessing%20where%20this%20is%20headed.%20Being%20too%20emotionally%20tied%20to%20an%20Nvidia%20investment%20(or%20any%20investment%2C%20really)%20can%20prevent%20people%20from%20being%20clear-eyed%20about%20the%20downsides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20risks.%20A%20handful%20of%20big%20companies%20are%20spending%20very%20aggressively%20on%20big%20AI%20bets%2C%20and%20if%20they're%20not%20getting%20the%20returns%20on%20that%20investment%20capital%20they%20expected%2C%20that%20spending%20could%20slow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20only%20a%20few%20companies%20that%20are%20making%20money%20off%20of%20generative%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20Mortonson%20said.%20If%20more%20companies%20don't%20start%20seeing%20some%20bang%20for%20their%20buck%2C%20he%20added%2C%20then%20at%20some%20point%20there%20may%20just%20be%20a%20pause%20in%20all%20the%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETechnologically%2C%20Nvidia%20is%20very%20far%20ahead%20of%20its%20competitors.%20It%20really%20is%20the%20only%20game%20in%20town%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20high-end%20chips%20it's%20producing.%20(The%20Department%20of%20Justice%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoj-subpoena-nvidia-antitrust-investigation-heats-up-report-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20also%20reportedly%20looking%20into%20this%20competition%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E.)%20But%20that%20probably%20won't%20last%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNvidia%2C%20I%20think%2C%20has%20a%20great%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20Schwarz%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20also%20think%20that%20people%20underestimate%20how%20all%20of%20Nvidia's%20biggest%20customers%20also%20make%20their%20own%20chips%20and%20have%20no%20interest%20in%20giving%20Nvidia%20all%20of%20their%20money%20forever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20superstar%20like%20Huang%20at%20the%20helm%20probably%20does%2C%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20calm%20some%20nerves.%20After%20all%2C%20Nvidia%20has%20been%20around%20since%201993%2C%20and%20he's%20been%20pretty%20prescient%20on%20all%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Jensen's%20flying%20the%20plane%2C%20institutional%20investors%20feel%20very%20comfortable%20sitting%20in%203A%2C%20drinking%20their%20cabernet%2C%26quot%3B%20Ives%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20obsession%20with%20Nvidia%20is%20not%20happening%20in%20a%20vacuum.%20The%20cultural%20vibe%20of%20the%20moment%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgambling-young-men-sports-betting-crypto-meme-stock-market-addiction-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Every%20much%20one%20of%20gambling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20sports%20betting%2C%20crypto%2C%20meme%20stocks%2C%20and%20even%20regular%20stocks%20are%20ways%20to%20get%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20dopamine%20hit%20you'd%20expect%20in%20a%20casino.%20Nvidia%20is%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20safer%20gambling-adjacent%20bets%20an%20investor%20can%20make%20(though%20options%20can%20be%20a%20different%20story).%20Nobody%20thinks%20that%20the%20company%20will%20disappear%20overnight%20or%20that%20its%20valuation%20will%20plummet.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20going%20all%20in%20on%20the%20mania%20around%20the%20company%20is%20without%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Redditor%20I%20talked%20to%20for%20this%20story%20wiped%20out%20his%20savings%20during%20the%20pandemic%20on%20risky%20investments%20and%20wound%20up%20having%20to%20dip%20into%20his%20401(k)%20to%20recover.%20He%20subsequently%20dumped%20that%20money%20into%20Nvidia%2C%20which%20has%20paid%20off.%20He%20estimates%20that%20about%2070%25%20of%20his%20liquid%20assets%20are%20in%20the%20stock%2C%20though%20its%20recent%20declines%20have%20made%20him%20think%20twice%20about%20that%20allocation.%20%26quot%3BIt%20still%20hurts%20to%20see%20the%20sharp%20drop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20Still%2C%20he's%20bought%20in%20%E2%80%94%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20he%20put%20a%20bunch%20of%20historical%20data%20on%20Nvidia%20into%20ChatGPT%20and%20asked%20it%20questions%20about%20various%20stock%20trends%20and%20highs%20and%20lows%2C%20and%20he%20felt%20reassured%20by%20the%20results.%20%26quot%3BUsually%20you%20pay%20for%20someone%20to%20provide%20you%20that%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20said%20ChatGPT's%20capabilities%20reinforced%20his%20belief%20in%20his%20thesis%20around%20Nvidia%20and%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20escaping%20Nvidia%20right%20now.%20It's%20Wall%20Street's%20Elvis%20or%20Zack%20Morris%20or%20Taylor%20Swift%20or%20Chappell%20Roan.%20The%20excitement%20around%20it%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20extra%2C%20and%20even%20if%20you%20want%20to%20avoid%20it%2C%20you%20can't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20accidentally%20poked%20the%20Nvidia%20fan%20bear%20by%20slightly%20making%20fun%20of%20one%20of%20the%20watch%20parties.%20People%20told%20me%20not%20to%20yuck%20their%20yum%2C%20said%20I%20was%20being%20a%20bummer%2C%20called%20me%20some%20names%20I%20will%20not%20repeat%20here.%20I%20recognize%20this%20was%20not%20my%20nicest%20moment%2C%20but%20you%20also%20have%20to%20admit%20that%20going%20to%20a%20bar%20to%20watch%20an%20earnings%20call%20is%20a%20little%20odd.%20But%20then%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Nvidia's%20earnings%2C%20I%20popped%20over%20to%20a%20friend's%20after%20work%20and%20noticed%20he%20had%20the%20TV%20on.%20I%20suggested%20he%20flip%20over%20to%20CNBC%20to%20see%20what%20had%20happened%20with%20Nvidia.%20I'm%20not%20a%20Nvidia%20true%20believer%2C%20but%20I'm%20apparently%20Nvidia%20curious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%2