is%20Document%20Is%20Missing...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court's%20Big%20Question%20In%20Kolkata%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20asked%20the%20CBI%20to%20file%20a%20fresh%20report%20in%20the%20case%20next%20Tuesday.%20The%20central%20agency%20today%20flagged%20the%20forensic%20report%20in%20the%20case%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bwho%20collected%20the%20samples%26quot%3B%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20relevant%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Mehta%20said%20the%20central%20agency%20had%20decided%20to%20send%20samples%20to%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20forensic%20examination%20report%20and%20one%20thing%20is%20admitted%20that%20when%20the%20girl%20was%20found%20at%209%3A30%20am%2C%20her%20jeans%20and%20undergarments%20were%20removed%20and%20lying%20nearby...%20semi-nude%20and%20injury%20marks%20also%20on%20body...%20they%20have%20taken%20samples.%20they%20have%20sent%20to%20CFSL%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20CBI%20has%20taken%20a%20decision%20to%20send%20the%20sample%20to%20AIIMS%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20explicitly%20mentioning%20the%20findings%2C%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPerson%20enters%2C%20girl%20is%20nude%20and%20this%20is%20the%20result%20of%20FSL.%20So%20who%20took%20the%20sample%20is%20relevant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725871800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fpk6v6rm_dy-chandrachud_625x300_20_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-lower-your-pitch-chief-justice-rebukes-lawyer-he-apologises-6524273%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20today%20asked%20a%20lawyer%20to%20lower%20his%20voice%20and%20asked%20if%20he%20was%20addressing%20the%20judges%20or%20the%20gallery%20outside%20the%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-lower-your-pitch-chief-justice-rebukes-lawyer-he-apologises-6524273%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPrevent%20Undue%20Panic%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre's%20Advisory%20To%20States%20On%20Mpox%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20on%20Monday%20recommended%20screening%20and%20testing%20of%20all%20suspected%20Mpox%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fmonkeypox%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonkeypox%3C%2Fa%3E%20patients%2C%20and%20isolation%20of%20confirmed%20cases%2C%20as%20well%20as%20contact%20tracing%20to%20%26quot%3Bprevent%20and%2For%20minimise%20risk%20of%20any%20case%20or%20death%20due%20to%20Mpox%20in%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStates%20and%20union%20territories%20have%20been%20urged%20to%20identify%20hospitals%20to%20prep%20isolation%20facilities%20and%20stand%20ready%20to%20receive%20suspected%20and%20confirmed%20cases%2C%20which%20will%20need%20increased%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20%26quot%3Bcrucial%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20government%20also%20said%20to%20guard%20against%C2%A0%26quot%3Bundue%20panic%20amongst%20the%20masses%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20the%20Health%20Ministry%20has%20recommended%20dissemination%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmohfw.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FGuidelines%2520for%2520Management%2520of%2520Monkeypox%2520Disease.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguidelines%20on%20%26quot%3Bmanagement%20of%20monkeypox%20disease%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20of%20a%20detailed%20surveillance%20strategy%20for%20tracking%20of%20suspected%20cases%20and%20contact%20tracing%20-%20similar%20to%20exhaustive%20measures%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20Covid%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20offered%20a%20list%20of%20%26quot%3Blaboratories%20operationalised%20to%20undertake%20testing%2C%20clinical%20management%20protocol%2C%20infection%20prevention%20and%20control%20practices%2C%20as%20well%20as%20risk%20communication%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20further%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Breview%20of%20public%20health%20preparedness%2C%20particularly%20at%20health%20facility%20level%20at%20state%20and%20districts%20by%20senior%20officials%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20should%20include%20briefing%20healthcare%20workers%2C%20%26quot%3Bespecially%20those%20working%20in%20skin%2FSTD%20(sexually%20transmitted%20disease)%20clinics%2C%20about%20symptoms%2C%20differential%20diagnoses%2C%20and%20action%20to%20be%20taken%20following%20detection%20of%20a%20Mpox%20case%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20information%20about%20Mpox%20and%20its%20common%20symptoms%20are%20widely%20available%2C%20the%20Health%20Ministry%20referred%20to%20the%20latest%20update%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%2C%20which%20indicated%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20monkeypox%20patients%20are%20men%20between%20the%20age%20of%2018%20and%2044%2C%20and%20present%20with%20rash%20(systemic%20or%20genital)%20followed%20by%20fever%20as%20the%20most%20common%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20Mpox%20was%20declared%20a%20PHEIC%2C%20or%20Public%20Health%20Emergency%20of%20International%20Concern%2C%20by%20the%20WHO%20which%20had%20assessed%20the%20risk%20of%20spread%20of%20the%20current%20outbreak%20from%20beyond%20Africa%2C%20where%20a%20surge%20in%20cases%20has%20been%20reported%20from%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20Congo%20and%20also%20from%20other%20nations%20like%20Burundi%2C%20Kenya%2C%20Rwanda%2C%20and%20Uganda.%20There%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-mpox-strain-mutating-very-rapidly-how-scientists-are-responding-6426881%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20new%20strain%20from%20the%20DRC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20scientists%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistans-peshawar-emerges-as-epicentre-of-mpox-as-tally-reaches-5-report-6467196%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPakistan's%20Peshawar%20Is%20Mpox%20'Epicentre'%3F%20Tally%20Reaches%205%3A%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20confirmed%20case%20has%20been%20reported%20from%20India%20so%20far%2C%20although%20five%20have%20been%20reported%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20according%20to%20Geo%20News.%C2%A0The%20latest%20patient%2C%20a%2047-year-old%20man%2C%20tested%20positive%20after%20being%20isolated%20by%20Border%20Health%20Services%20staff%20on%20August%2029.%20He%20had%20returned%20from%20the%20Gulf%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-1st-mpox-case-centre-says-man-isolated-no-cause-for-alarm-6518374%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia's%201st%20Mpox%20Case%3F%20Centre%20Says%20Man%20Isolated%2C%20No%20Cause%20For%20Alarm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20a%20man%20who%20recently%20returned%20from%20a%20country%20where%20confirmed%20cases%20have%20been%20reported%20was%20isolated%20on%20Sunday%20and%20his%20samples%20are%20being%20tested.%20His%20conditions%20is%20reported%20as%20stable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20WHO%2C%20so%20far%20over%20120%20countries%20have%20reported%20Mpox%20cases%20from%20January%202022%20to%20August%202024.%20There%20have%20been%20over%20100%2C000%20lab-confirmed%20cases%20and%20around%20220%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fserum-institute-says-working-to-develop-monkeypox-vaccine-6379320%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESerum%20Institute%20Says%20Working%20To%20Develop%20Monkeypox%20Vaccine%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20says%20a%20vaccine%20can%20help%20prevent%20infection%20and%20can%20also%20be%20administered%20after%20a%20person%20has%20been%20in%20contact%20with%20someone%20who%20has%20Mpox.%20%26quot%3BIn%20these%20cases%2C%20the%20vaccine%20should%20be%20given%20less%20than%20four%20days%20after%20contact%20(and)%20can%20be%20given%20for%20up%20to%2014%20days%20if%20the%20person%20has%20no%20symptoms...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725871440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F1n5d9p5_mpox-reuters_625x300_24_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fscreening-and-testing-contact-tracing-centres-mpox-advisory-to-states-6523921%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20recommended%20screening%20and%20testing%20of%20all%20suspected%20Mpox%2C%20or%20monkeypox%20patients%2C%20and%20isolation%20of%20confirmed%20cases%2C%20as%20well%20as%20contact%20tracing%20to%20%26quot%3Bprevent%20and%2For%20minimise%20risk%20of%20any%20case%20or%20death%20due%20to%20Mpox%20in%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fscreening-and-testing-contact-tracing-centres-mpox-advisory-to-states-6523921%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20This%20Document%20Is%20Missing...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court's%20Big%20Question%20In%20Kolkata%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20key%20document%20necessary%20for%20post-mortem%20came%20under%20the%20spotlight%20today%20as%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20heard%20the%20Kolkata%20doctor's%20rape%20and%20murder%20case.%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20questioned%20where%20the%20challan%20was%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20an%20autopsy%20cannot%20be%20carried%20out%20without%20it.%20Senior%20Advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%2C%20submitted%20that%20he%20could%20not%20find%20the%20document%20immediately%20and%20would%20get%20back%20to%20the%20court%20on%20this%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20came%20up%20after%20an%20advocate%20appearing%20in%20the%20matter%20asked%20if%20the%20clothes%20of%20the%20victim%20were%20produced%20during%20the%20autopsy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20then%20asked%20about%20the%20document%20when%20the%20body%20was%20handed%20over%20for%20autopsy%20after%20the%20inquest.%20When%20Mr%20Sibal%20said%20he%20is%20not%20immediately%20able%20to%20locate%20it%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20important%20because%20it%20has%20a%20column%20showing%20what%20clothes%20and%20articles%20were%20sent%20along%20with%20the%20body%2C%20we%20want%20to%20see%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post-mortem%20team%2C%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said%2C%20will%20not%20accept%20the%20body%20without%20the%20challan.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20why%20we%20want%20to%20see%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sibal%20requested%20the%20court%20for%20more%20time.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20submit%20it%20to%20the%20court.%20What%20I%20am%20told%20is%20that%20CJM%20(Chief%20Judicial%20Magistrate)%20filled%20it%20up%20himself%20and%20sent%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWas%20the%20post-mortem%20carried%20out%20without%20the%20request%20form%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20asked%2C%20and%20Solicitor%20General%20Mehta%20added%20that%20is%20not%20possible%20because%20it%20is%20a%20statutory%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20JB%20Pardiwala%2C%20who%20was%20on%20the%20three-judge%20bench%20along%20with%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20pointed%20to%20the%20post-mortem%20report.%20%26quot%3BSee%20the%20third%20column%20on%20the%20top%2C%20the%20constable%20(who%20brought%20the%20body)%20is%20supposed%20to%20carry%20this%20(form).%20It%20has%20been%20struck%20off.%20So%20there%20is%20no%20reference%20of%20this%20challan%20when%20the%20dead%20body%20is%20sent%20for%20examination.%20You%20need%20to%20explain%2C%20if%20this%20document%20is%20missing%2C%20then%20something%20is%20amiss%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20then%20said%20that%20the%20CBI%20should%20ask%20for%20this%20document%20from%20the%20Bengal%20government%20too.%20An%20advocate%20appearing%20before%20the%20bench%20said%20this%20document%20was%20submitted%20during%20the%20hearing%20in%20Calcutta%20High%20Court.%20The%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20then%20questioned%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20absence%20of%20mention%20in%20the%20post-mortem%20report%2C%20the%20possibility%20of%20it%20having%20been%20created%20subsequently%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sibal%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20being%20created%20subsequently.%20We%20will%20file%20an%20affidavit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20has%20been%20apprised%20of%20challan%20when%20the%20body%20is%20examined.%20CBI%20states%20that%20the%20above%20challan%20duly%20filled%20in%20is%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20case%20file%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20CBI.%20Faced%20with%20the%20above%2C%20the%20advocate%20appearing%20for%20one%20of%20the%20petitioners%20before%20the%20high%20court%20says%20the%20form%20was%20produced%20before%20the%20high%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20in%20its%20order%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20counsel%20appearing%20for%20the%20Bengal%20government%20do%20not%20have%20the%20document%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCopy%20of%20the%20form%20duly%20filled%20in%20will%20be%20submitted%20on%20the%20next%20date%20of%20hearing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20now%20asked%20the%20CBI%20to%20file%20a%20fresh%20report%20in%20the%20case%20next%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agency%20today%20flagged%20the%20forensic%20report%20in%20the%20case%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bwho%20collected%20the%20samples%26quot%3B%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20relevant%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20Mehta%20said%20the%20central%20agency%20had%20decided%20to%20send%20samples%20to%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20forensic%20examination%20report%20and%20one%20thing%20is%20admitted%20that%20when%20the%20girl%20was%20found%20at%209%3A30%20am%2C%20her%20jeans%20and%20undergarments%20were%20removed%20and%20lying%20nearby...%20semi-nude%20and%20injury%20marks%20also%20on%20body...%20they%20have%20taken%20samples.%20they%20have%20sent%20to%20CFSL%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20CBI%20has%20taken%20a%20decision%20to%20send%20the%20sample%20to%20AIIMS%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20explicitly%20mentioning%20the%20findings%2C%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BPerson%20enters%2C%20girl%20is%20nude%20and%20this%20is%20the%20result%20of%20FSL.%20So%20who%20took%20the%20sample%20is%20relevant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20delay%20in%20filing%20the%20FIR%20came%20up%20again.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20delay%20of%20almost%2014%20hours%20in%20recording%20the%20FIR.%20It%20is%20very%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725871440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsubmit-fresh-status-report-next-tuesday-supreme-court-to-cbi-on-kolkata-horror-6523228%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20asked%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%2