re%20not%20going%20to%20accept%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20interaction%20with%20the%20students%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20low%20female%20labour%20participation%20in%20India.%20In%20his%20reply%2C%20he%20pointed%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20attitude%26quot%3B%20Indian%20males%20have%20towards%20women.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Indian%20males%2C%20attitude%20towards%20women%20is%20ridiculous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20change%20the%20mindset%20to%20think%20of%20women%20the%20same%20way%20we%20think%20of%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20also%20said%20the%20attitude%20towards%20women%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20ideological%20fight%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Opposition.%20%26quot%3BBJP%2FRSS%20believe%20that%20women%20should%20be%20restricted%20to%20a%20particular%20role%2C%20they%20should%20stay%20at%20home%2C%20cook%20food%2C%20they%20should%20not%20talk%20too%20much%2C%20we%20believe%20women%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20aspire%20to%20whatever%20they%20want%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20also%20spoke%20on%20unemployment%20in%20India%20and%20drew%20a%20comparison%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20West%20has%20an%20employment%20problem.%20India%20has%20an%20employment%20problem...%20But%20many%20countries%20in%20the%20world%20don't%20have%20an%20employment%20problem.%20China%20certainly%20doesn't%20have%20an%20employment%20problem.%20Vietnam%20doesn't%20have%20an%20employment%20problem.%20So%20there%20are%20places%20on%20the%20planet%20that%20are%20not%20struggling%20with%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20reason.%20If%20you%20look%20at%20the%20United%20States%20in%20the%201940s%2C%2050s%20and%2060s%2C%20they%20were%20the%20centre%20of%20global%20production.%20Anything%20that%20was%20made%2C%20cars%2C%20washing%20machines%2C%20TVs%2C%20all%20made%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20Production%20moved%20from%20the%20United%20States.%20It%20went%20to%20Korea%2C%20it%20went%20to%20Japan.%20Eventually%2C%20it%20went%20to%20China.%20If%20you%20look%20today%2C%20China%20is%20dominating%20global%20production...%20So%20what%20has%20happened%3F%20The%20West%2C%20America%2C%20Europe%2C%20and%20India%20have%20given%20up%20on%20the%20idea%20of%20production%20and%20they've%20handed%20it%20to%20China.%20The%20act%20of%20production%20creates%20jobs.%20What%20we%20do%2C%20what%20the%20Americans%20do%2C%20what%20the%20West%20does%2C%20is%20we%20organise%20consumption%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Hits%20Back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi's%20remarks%20have%20drawn%20strong%20remarks%20from%20the%20BJP.%20The%20ruling%20party's%20national%20spokesperson%20Pradeep%20Bhandari%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20is%20%26quot%3Beager%20to%20bat%20for%20China%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20it%20because%20of%20his%20MoU%20with%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%20that%20he%20always%20bats%20for%20China%20and%20does%20not%20bat%20for%20India%3F%20Rahul%20does%20not%20stop%20here%2C%20he%20attacks%20the%20Indian%20legal%20system%20just%20because%20he%20is%20out%20on%20bail.%20He%20predicts%20social%20tension%20in%20India%20just%20because%20it%20is%20his%20strategy%20to%20divide%20and%20rule%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhandari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSam%20Pitroda%20says%20that%20he%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20'Pappu'.%20He%20has%20become%20very%20evil%20now%20because%20all%20his%20statements%20reflect%20falsehood%20against%20India%2C%20all%20his%20statements%20reflect%20a%20man%20who%20wants%20to%20divide%20society%20and%20a%20man%20who%20wants%20to%20bat%20for%20the%20Chinese.%20He%20insults%20the%20Hindu%20gods%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20God.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20INDI%20Alliance%20is%20always%20against%20Sanatana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20essence%20of%20Rahul's%20speech%20is%2C%20it%20is%20against%20Bharat%2C%20against%20the%20women%20of%20India%20and%20it%20is%20everything%20that%20China%20or%20any%20other%20power%20want%20to%20further%20their%20agenda%20in%20India.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20people%20of%20India%20rejected%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Congress%20in%202014%2C%202019%20and%202024.%20They%20will%20continue%20to%20reject%20it%20in%202029%20and%20choose%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725871380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fi4o6noq8_rahul-gandhi-ani_625x300_09_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-says-fear-of-pm-gone-bjp-flags-habit-of-insulting-india-6523040%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20tore%20into%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideological%20parent%20RSS%20in%20public%20addresses%20in%20Dallas%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20spoke%20on%20wide-ranging%20issues%20in%20his%20interactions%20with%20students%20at%20University%20of%20Texas%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-says-fear-of-pm-gone-bjp-flags-habit-of-insulting-india-6523040%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%2C%20UAE%20Crown%20Prince%20Meet%20In%20Delhi%2C%20Hold%20Bilateral%20Talks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Crown%20Prince%20of%20Abu%20Dhabi%20has%20met%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20in%20New%20Delhi%20as%20he%20begins%20his%20first%20official%20trip%20to%20India%20as%20the%20Crown%20Prince.%20The%20two%20leaders%20have%20begun%20talks%20to%20further%20bilateral%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20received%20Crown%20Prince%20Sheikh%20Kh