and%2C%20we%20also%20need%20the%20evolutionary%20leaps%20of%20Founder%20Mode%2C%20where%20a%20Steve%20Jobs%2C%20or%20a%20Jensen%20Huang%2C%20or%20an%20Elon%20Musk%20comes%20around%20to%20shake%20things%20up%2C%20creating%20ungodly%20inventions%20that%20would%20never%20be%20conceived%20by%20a%20manager.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22NIRMALYA%20DUTTA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhy-companies-need-both-manager-mode-and-founder-mode-to-succeed%2Farticleshow%2F113185509.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BProsecutor%20vs%20Convicted%20Felon%26quot%3B%3A%20The%20Donald%20Trump-Kamala%20Harris%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20hostile%20exchanges%20between%20prosecutor%20and%20felon%2C%20Kamala%20Harris%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20are%20old%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Tuesday's%20high-stakes%20debate%20will%20be%20new%20territory%20for%20the%20Democratic%20vice%20president%20and%20her%20Republican%20rival%2C%20due%20to%20meet%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20front%20of%20a%20prime-time%20television%20audience%20of%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20striking%20thing%20about%20this%20debate%20is%2C%20it's%20the%20first%20time%20in%20history%20where%20we'll%20see%20a%20prosecutor%20and%20convicted%20felon%20facing%20off%20against%20each%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Koneschusky%2C%20a%20PR%20expert%20and%20former%20press%20secretary%20for%20US%20Senate%20leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20an%20incredible%20contrast.%20I%20wouldn't%20expect%20a%20lot%20of%20intricate%20policy%20discussion.%20I%20expect%20we'll%20see%20more%20style%20than%20substance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20of%20debating%20technique%20identify%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%2078%2C%20as%20an%20avid%20proponent%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BGish%20Gallop%2C%26quot%3B%20named%20for%20Duane%20Gish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGish%2C%20who%20defended%20as%20literally%20true%20the%20Biblical%20account%20of%20the%20world's%20creation%20in%20six%20days%2C%20would%20overwhelm%20opponents%20with%20a%20dizzying%20torrent%20of%20rapid-fire%20falsehoods%2C%20distortions%20and%20distractions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20--%20who%20is%20not%20known%20to%20have%20a%20granular%20grasp%20of%20policy%20--%20owes%20much%20of%20his%20success%20to%20this%20kind%20of%20filibustering%2C%20as%20he%20packs%20conspiracy%20theory%2C%20anecdote%20and%20aside%20into%20an%20arcane%2C%20rebuttal-proof%20word%20salad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20hard%20to%20debate%20someone%20who%20is%20quickly%20changing%20topics%20and%20not%20fully%20or%20truthfully%20answering%20the%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Flavio%20Hickel%2C%20a%20politics%20professor%20at%20Maryland%20liberal%20arts%20school%20Washington%20College.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20%26quot%3BGish%20Gallop%26quot%3B%20may%20be%20good%20at%20putting%20opponents%20on%20the%20back%20foot%2C%20it%20is%20a%20risky%20strategy%20for%20someone%20trying%20to%20look%20presidential%2C%20analysts%20warn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Certainty%20and%20strength'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20debater%2C%20Trump%20brings%20energy%2C%20conveys%20certainty%20and%20strength%2C%20and%20never%20admits%20error%2C%20which%20translates%20for%20many%20people%20into%20presidential%20qualities%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Donald%20Nieman%2C%20a%20political%20analyst%20and%20professor%20at%20Binghamton%20University%20in%20New%20York%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20coupled%20with%20transparent%20lies%2C%20wild%20exaggerations%2C%20unseemly%20ad%20hominem%20attacks%20and%20loopy%20digressions%20that%20have%20the%20opposite%20effect%2C%20especially%20on%20the%20few%20undecided%20voters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20rose%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Democratic%20ticket%20after%2081-year-old%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20dismal%20debate%20performance%20against%20Trump%20led%20to%20him%20dropping%20out%20of%20the%20race%20amid%20questions%20around%20his%20advanced%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20expect%20the%2059-year-old%20Californian%20--%20%26quot%3BKamala%20the%20Cop%26quot%3B%20to%20her%20admirers%20--%20to%20lean%20into%20her%20experience%20as%20a%20district%20attorney%20and%20press%20Trump%20on%20his%20role%20in%20the%20deadly%202021%20insurrection%20at%20the%20US%20Capitol%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20multiple%20criminal%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHarris%20is%20a%20sharp%20prosecutor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Keith%20Gaddie%2C%20a%20politics%20professor%20at%20Texas%20Christian%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20showed%20her%20chops%20debating%20Biden%20and%20others%20in%202020%2C%20and%20will%20likely%20lean%20into%20a%20combination%20of%20tricks%20used%20by%20prosecutors%20to%20control%20witnesses%2C%20while%20also%20cultivating%20'jury%20sympathy.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Harris's%20ascension%2C%20Democrats'%20messaging%20has%20evolved%20from%20presenting%20Trump%20as%20a%20powerful%20and%20existential%20threat%20to%20democracy%20to%20minimizing%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bweird%26quot%3B%20and%20small.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKoneschusky%20expects%20to%20see%20more%20of%20this%20in%20the%20debate%2C%20but%20warned%20that%20Harris%20faces%20a%20balancing%20act%20between%20going%20after%20her%20opponent%20and%20using%20her%20precious%20airtime%20to%20make%20her%20own%20pitch%20for%20the%20Oval%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFormer%20prosecutor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20this%20is%20a%20chance%20for%20Harris%20to%20define%20herself%2C%20and%20she%20needs%20to%20fully%20capitalize%20on%20that%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it's%20also%20important%20that%20Harris%20prosecutes%20the%20case%20against%20Trump%20in%20this%20debate%2C%20and%20she's%20well-equipped%20to%20do%20so%20as%20a%20former%20prosecutor.%20This%20is%20something%20Biden%20failed%20to%20do%20in%20the%20last%20debate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Harris's%20standout%20debate%20moments%20came%20against%20Biden%2C%20ironically%2C%20in%20the%202019-20%20Democratic%20presidential%20nominating%20contest%2C%20when%20she%20took%20her%20then-rival%20to%20task%20for%20his%20opposition%20to%20using%20federal%20funds%20to%20desegregate%20schools%20through%20busing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20little%20girl%20in%20California%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20second%20class%20to%20integrate%20her%20public%20schools%2C%20and%20she%20was%20bused%20to%20school%20every%20day.%20And%20that%20little%20girl%20was%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Harris%20said%2C%20in%20a%20moment%20that%20immediately%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20short-lived%202020%20bid%20for%20the%20White%20House%20also%20illustrated%20weaknesses%2C%20as%20when%20she%20allowed%20herself%20to%20be%20rattled%20by%20former%20Hawaii%20congresswoman%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%2C%20who%20savaged%20Harris%20over%20her%20record%20as%20a%20prosecutor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGabbard%20has%20switched%20sides%20and%20Trump%20has%20been%20using%20her%20in%20his%20debate%20prep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20muted%20microphones%20during%20the%20Trump%20debate%20may%20meanwhile%20deprive%20Harris%20of%20another%20strength%20--%20her%20ability%20to%20shut%20down%20rivals%20when%20they%20try%20to%20interrupt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarris%20deployed%20this%20to%20full%20effect%20when%20Mike%20Pence%20tried%20to%20cut%20her%20off%20during%20their%202020%20vice-presidential%20debate%20and%20she%20stopped%20him%20dead%20with%20an%20ice-cold%2C%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Vice%20President%2C%20I'm%20speaking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20