3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20broadcaster%2C%20these%20consultants%20illegally%20registered%20students%20for%20three-year%20courses%20at%20vocational%20or%20technical%20schools.%20Such%20institutions%20typically%20offer%20high%20school-equivalent%20certificates%20for%20skilled%20labor%20and%20are%20the%20gateway%20for%20entering%20fields%20like%20IT%20or%20electronics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20consultancy%20staff%20spoke%20to%20CCTV%20on%20camera%2C%20saying%20that%20they%20would%20use%20the%20%242%2C800%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Brelationship%20fee%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20present%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20go%20to%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20consultant%20said%20in%20one%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broadcaster%20kept%20all%20of%20its%20interviewees%20anonymous%2C%20as%20is%20the%20norm%20for%20Chinese%20media%20when%20dealing%20with%20people%20who%20aren't%20celebrities%20or%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20just%20need%20the%20student's%20residency%20registration%2C%20their%20personal%20information%2C%20a%20photo%20with%20a%20blue%20background%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20consultant%20said.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20after%20paying%20the%20fee%2C%20we'll%20sign%20a%20contract%2C%20and%20we'll%20give%20you%20the%20school%20registration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20said%20on%20camera%20that%20they%20could%20help%20their%20clients%20find%20schools%20with%20vacancies%20or%20establish%20ties%20with%20institutions%20chosen%20by%20the%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270d5dc72-f84f-4ea0-b4a6-dcc4e42d93eb%5C%22%3EChina%20finds%20schools%20offering%20the%20same%20services%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broadcaster%20also%20published%20footage%20of%20staff%20from%20five%20schools%20in%20the%20same%20regions%20directly%20offering%20%26quot%3Bempty%20student%20status.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20schools%2C%20spread%20across%20the%20automotive%2C%20aviation%2C%20IT%2C%20and%20engineering%20industries%2C%20said%20on%20camera%20that%20%26quot%3Bempty%20students%26quot%3B%20would%20only%20have%20to%20be%20present%20for%20one%20roll%20call%20per%20semester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20said%20they%20could%20arrange%20for%20the%20student%20to%20take%20entire%20semesters%20of%20medical%20leave.%20One%20school%20asked%20that%20the%20client%20clock%20in%20daily%20with%20a%20card%2C%20though%20they%20would%20not%20have%20to%20attend%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20school's%20staff%20said%20the%20student%20could%20record%20their%20attendance%20through%20a%20mobile%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20institutions%20would%20typically%20limit%20%26quot%3Bempty%20student%26quot%3B%20clients%20to%20a%20small%20proportion%20of%20an%20attending%20class%2C%20with%20one%20staff%20saying%20they%20would%20accept%20about%20three%20clients%20per%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECCTV's%20report%20is%20the%20latest%20of%20several%20to%20recently%20gain%20widespread%20attention%20on%20Chinese%20social%20media%2C%20becoming%20the%20top-most%20discussed%20post%20on%20Weibo%2C%20China's%20version%20of%20X%2C%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%2C%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.163.com%2Fdy%2Farticle%2FJ14U7M38053469LG.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etried%20to%20crack%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%26quot%3Bempty%20student%26quot%3B%20fraud%2C%20though%20the%20bulk%20of%20its%20attention%20has%20focused%20on%20students%20cheating%20on%20national%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20the%20scam%20is%20most%20well-known%20as%20a%20way%20to%20circumvent%20a%20national%20law%20that%20restricts%20students%20to%20schools%20inside%20their%20registered%20region%20of%20residency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fedu.people.com.cn%2Fn%2F2014%2F1222%2Fc1006-26248436.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPrevious%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20featured%20wealthy%20students%20who%20would%20%26quot%3Bmigrate%26quot%3B%20to%20less%20