%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66de6c24a0ff598b2665a928%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussia%20is%20facing%20a%20yuan%20shortage.%3Cp%3EVyacheslav%20Prokofyev%2FPool%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERussian%20banks%20are%20urging%20the%20country's%20central%20bank%20to%20boost%20yuan%20liquidity%20amid%20shortages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Russia's%20central%20bank%20is%20advising%20lenders%20to%20limit%20yuan-denominated%20loans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Russian%20central%20bank%20said%20currency%20swaps%20are%20a%20short-term%2C%20not%20a%20long-term%20solution%20to%20yuan%20supply.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20central%20bank%20and%20lenders%20are%20asking%20each%20other%20to%20preserve%20the%20country's%20stash%20of%20Chinese%20yuan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Thursday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Frussia-economy-china-yuan-sanctions-bank-payments-trade-transfers-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20banks%3C%2Fa%3E%20complained%20that%20they've%20run%20out%20of%20the%20Chinese%20yuan%20and%20called%20on%20the%20Central%20Bank%20of%20Russia%20to%20increase%20liquidity%20through%20currency%20swaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Russia's%20central%20bank%20is%20passing%20the%20buck%20back%20to%20the%20country's%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcbr.snowball-income.com%2FCollection%2FCollection%2FFile%2F50609%2FORFR_2024-08.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20on%20Friday%2C%20Russia's%20central%20bank%20advised%20lenders%20to%20limit%20the%20issuance%20of%20yuan-denominated%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20bank%20is%20a%20primary%20source%20of%20yuan%20liquidity%20tha