ee%20grew%20the%20business%20from%20eight%20stores%20to%20over%202%2C600%20across%20Malaysia%2C%20the%20largest%20mini-mart%20chain%20in%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELee%20Thiam%20Wah%20started%20selling%20snacks%20at%20a%20roadside%20stall.%20Now%2C%20he's%20Asia's%20latest%20entrepreneur%20to%20reach%20billionaire%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20founded%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fthe-convenience-store-market-in-malaysia-2019-2022-the-industry-is-witnessing-fast-developments-and-presents-huge-potential-for-convenience-store-players-1029242346%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econvenience%20store%3C%2Fa%3E%20chain%2099%20Speed%20Mart%20and%20officially%20became%20a%20billionaire%20on%20Monday%20after%20his%20company%20went%20public%20in%20Kuala%20Lumpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%24531%20million%20initial%20public%20offering%20on%20Monday%20shattered%20a%20seven-year%20record%20in%20the%20country%20for%20the%20largest%20IPO%2C%20at%201.65%20Malaysian%20ringgit%2C%20or%20%240.38%2C%20per%20share.%20This%20brings%20Lee's%20net%20worth%20to%20%243.3%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-09-08%2Fmalaysia-s-biggest-ipo-in-7-years-to-turn-99-speed-mart-founder-into-billionaire%3Fsrnd%3Dhomepage-asia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Billionaires%20Index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201964%20in%20the%20Malaysian%20city%20of%20Klang%2C%20Lee%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20family%20with%2011%20children.%20His%20parents%2C%20a%20construction%20worker%20and%20a%20hawker%2C%20struggled%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%2C%20per%20Bloomberg.%20Lee%20contracted%20polio%20as%20a%20child%20and%20lost%20the%20use%20of%20his%20legs%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20find%20work.%20He%20turned%20to%20entrepreneurship%2C%20selling%20snacks%20from%20a%20stall%20to%20support%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20to%20help%20myself.%20Nobody%20would%20hire%20me%20due%20to%20my%20physical%20limitation%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fglobal%2F2010%2F0315%2Fentrepreneurs-malaysia-speedsmart-handicaps-king-of-mini-marts.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20opened%20his%20first%20grocery%20store%20in%201987%20at%20the%20age%20of%2023.%20Over%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20his%20business%20grew%20into%20a%20chain%20of%20eight%20stores%20under%20the%20name%20Pasar%20Mini%2099.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELee's%20wife%2C%20Ng%20Lee%20Tieng%2C%20joined%20the%20company%20in%201997%20as%20a%20purchasing%20executive.%20Together%2C%20they%20built%20what%20would%20become%20the%20largest%20mini-mart%20chain%20in%20Malaysia%2C%20with%202%2C651%20stores%20nationwide%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company's%20IPO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fanns.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com%2F3473571.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprospectus%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20this%20week's%20IPO%2C%20the%20couple%20fully%20owned%20the%20business.%20Lee%20will%20remain%20its%20majority%20shareholder%2C%20controlling%20up%20to%20a%20combined%2079.7%25%20stake.%20He%20will%20continue%20as%20the%20company's%20CEO.%20Ng%20will%20hold%20a%203.2%25%20stake%20in%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20a%2040%25%20share%20of%20the%20mini-mart%20market%20in%20Malaysia%20and%20controls%20nearly%2012%25%20of%20the%20overall%20grocery%20sector%2C%20according%20to%20the%20prospectus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IPO%20attracted%2014%20major%20investors%2C%20including%20firms%20like%20abrdn%20Asia%20and%20UOB%20Asset%20Management%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported.%20The%20company%20plans%20to%20use%20over%20half%20of%20its%20IPO%20proceeds%20to%20add%20another%20250%20stores%20a%20year%20until%20it%20reaches%20about%203%2C000%20outlets%20in%20three%20years%2C%20set%20up%20new%20distribution%20centers%2C%20and%20purchase%20new%20delivery%20trucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20saw%20a%20second-quarter%20profit%20of%20125.5%20ringgit%20%E2%80%94%20a%2066.3%25%20year-over-year%20increase%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fretail-consumer%2F99-speed-mart-opens-121-higher-debut-malaysias-biggest-ipo-7-years-2024-09-09%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3D99%2520Speed%2520Mart%252C%2520founded%2520by%2C%252C%25202023%252C%2520its%2520prospectus%2520showed.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20Monday.%2099%20Speed%20Mart%20also%20posted%20a%20revenue%20of%20over%209%2C000%20million%20ringgit%20in%202023%2C%20over%20four%20times%20that%20of%20its%20main%20competitor%2C%207-Eleven%20Malaysia%2C%20per%20its%20IPO%20prospectus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E99%20Speed%20Mart%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flee-thiam-wah-asia-newest-billionaire-99-speed-mart-ipo-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725859870000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66de7f4e83b8099cf9fca782%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flee-thiam-wah-asia-newest-billionaire-99-speed-mart-ipo-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lee%20Thiam%20Wah%2C%20founder%20of%2099%20Speed%20Mart%2C%20became%20Asia's%20latest%20billionaire%2C%20with%20the%20largest%20Malaysian%20IPO%20in%20seven%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lwee%40insider.com%20(Lian%20Kit%20Wee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A130%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flee-thiam-wah-asia-newest-billionaire-99-speed-mart-ipo-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Before%20his%20death%2C%20Steve%20Jobs%20told%20Bob%20Iger%20to%20retire%20from%20Disney%20and%20try%20to%20enjoy%20the%20good%20things%20