atti%20Scialfa%2C%20Bruce%20Springsteen%E2%80%99s%20wife%20and%20E%20Street%20bandmate%2C%20has%20revealed%20she%20was%20diagnosed%20in%202018%20with%20multiple%20myeloma%2C%20a%20form%20of%20blood%20cancer.%20Scialfa%20addressed%20her%20diagnosis%20in%20the%20new%20documentary%20%E2%80%9CRoad%20Diary%3A%20Bruce%20Springsteen%20and%20The%20E%20Street%20Band%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20premiered%20on%20Sunday%20night%20at%20the%20Toronto%20Film%20Festival.%20In%20the%20film%2C%20a%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rebecca%20Rubin%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fpatti-scialfa-cancer-diagnosis-bruce-springsteen-e-street-band-1236137754%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLove%2C%20Respect%2C%20Humility%20Missing%20In%20Indian%20Politics%26quot%3B%3A%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELove%2C%20respect%20and%20humility%20are%20missing%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20said%20in%20his%20address%20to%20the%20Indian%20American%20community%20in%20Texas%2C%20where%20he%20also%20criticised%20the%20RSS%20for%20believing%20that%20India%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20idea%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20made%20the%20remarks%20on%20Sunday%20in%20Dallas%20during%20his%20first%20interaction%20with%20Indian%20expatriates%20after%20becoming%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRSS%20believes%20that%20India%20is%20one%20idea.%20We%20believe%20that%20India%20is%20a%20multiplicity%20of%20ideas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20much%20like%20the%20United%20States%2C%20we%20believe%20everybody%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20participate.%20We%20believe%20that%20everybody%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20dream%2C%20(and)%20everybody%20should%20be%20given%20space%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20caste%2C%20language%2C%20religion%2C%20tradition%2C%20history%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20fight.%20The%20fight%20crystallised%20in%20the%20election%20when%20millions%20of%20people%20in%20India%20clearly%20understood%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20was%20attacking%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20Because%20what%20I%20am%20saying%20to%20you%20is%20the%20union%20of%20states%2C%20respect%20to%20languages%2C%20respect%20to%20religions%2C%20respect%20to%20traditions%2C%20respect%20to%20caste.%20This%20is%20all%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Gandhi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20his%20role%20was%20to%20inject%20values%20of%20love%2C%20respect%20and%20humility%20into%20Indian%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20what%20is%20missing%20in%20our%20political%20systems%20and%20across%20parties%20is%20love%2C%20respect%20and%20humility.%20Love%20to%20all%20human%20beings%2C%20not%20necessarily%20only%20people%20of%20one%20religion%2C%20one%20community%2C%20one%20caste%2C%20one%20State%2C%20or%20to%20those%20who%20speak%20one%20language%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRespect%20to%20everybody%20who%20is%20trying%20to%20build%20an%20India%2C%20not%20just%20the%20most%20powerful%2C%20but%20the%20weakest%20and%20humility%2C%20not%20in%20others%2C%20but%20in%20oneself.%20I%20think%20that%20is%20how%20I%20see%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20an%20indirect%20reference%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20failed%20to%20get%20a%20majority%20on%20its%20own%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20were%20saying%20the%20BJP%20is%20attacking%20our%20tradition%2C%20attacking%20our%20language%2C%20etc.%20What%20they%20understood%20was%20that%20anybody%20who%20is%20attacking%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20is%20also%20attacking%20our%20religious%20tradition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20that%20immediately%2C%20within%20minutes%20of%20the%20election%20result%2C%20nobody%20in%20India%20was%20scared%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20These%20are%20huge%20achievements.%20These%20are%20huge%20achievements%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%20who%20realised%20democracy%2C%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%20who%20realised%20that%20we%20are%20not%20going%20to%20accept%20an%20attack%20on%20our%20Constitution.%20We're%20not%20going%20to%20accept%20an%20attack%20on%20our%20religion.%20We're%20not%20going%20to%20accept%20an%20attack%20on%20our%20States%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20the%20US%20needs%20India%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20the%20Indian%20expatriates%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bbridge%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20view%2C%20you%20should%20travel%20freely%20between%20these%20two%20homes.%20You%20should%20bring%20the%20idea%20of%20India%20to%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20ideas%20of%20the%20United%20States%20to%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Gandhi%20said%20in%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20a%20very%20important%20role%20because%20the%20relationship%20between%20these%20two%20unions%20is%20going%20to%20determine%20the%20future%20of%20both%E2%80%9D%20the%20countries%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725856200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F6fcll2e_rahul-gandhi-in-us_625x300_09_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flove-respect-humility-missing-in-indian-politics-rahul-gandhi-6522372%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Love%2C%20respect%20and%20humility%20are%20missing%20in%20Indian%20politics%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%2