8Road%20Diary%E2%80%99%3A%20%E2%80%98If%20I%20Went%20Tomorrow%2C%20It%E2%80%99s%20OK.%20What%20a%20F%E2%80%93king%20Ride!%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725855991000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fbruce-springsteen-billionaire-e1721401221249.png%3Fw%3D843%26h%3D561%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236137502%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Toronto%20welcomed%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Boss%E2%80%9D%20on%20Sunday%20night.%20But%20it%20was%20a%20more%20contemplative%20Bruce%20Springsteen%20on%20display%20at%20the%20Roy%20Thomson%20Hall%20for%20the%20world%20premiere%20of%20%E2%80%9CRoad%20Diary%3A%20Bruce%20Springsteen%20and%20The%20E%20Street%20Band%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20look%20at%20the%20rock%20legend%20and%20his%20tight-knit%20group%20of%20collaborators%2C%20which%20also%20served%20as%20a%20meditation%20on%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Varietybrentlang%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fmarkets-festivals%2Fbruce-springsteen-mortality-toronto-film-festival-new-documentary-road-diary-e-street-band-premiere-1236137502%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20Official%20Lists%20Big%20Roadblocks%20In%20Its%20Probe%20Into%20Kolkata%20Rape-Murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20month%20since%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20was%20found%20raped%20and%20killed%20at%20a%20seminar%20hall%20in%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%20The%20incident%20has%20sparked%20nationwide%20outrage%20and%20every%20corner%20of%20Bengal%20has%20witnessed%20massive%20rallies%20demanding%20justice%20in%20the%20case.%20The%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20government%20has%20come%20under%20the%20scanner%20for%20its%20handling%20of%20the%20case%20and%20accused%20of%20shielding%20the%20accused%20and%20attempting%20a%20cover-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20following%20a%20petition%20from%20the%20victims'%20parents%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20transferred%20the%20sensitive%20case%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%20But%20nearly%20four%20weeks%20after%20the%20central%20agency%20took%20over%20the%20probe%2C%20there%20have%20been%20no%20more%20arrests%20apart%20from%20Sanjay%20Roy%2C%20in%20the%20rape-murder%20case.%20A%20civic%20volunteer%20who%20frequented%20the%20case%2C%20Roy%20was%20arrested%20by%20Kolkata%20Police%20a%20day%20after%20the%20incident%20and%20CBI%20took%20his%20custody%20later.%20The%20CBI%20has%20arrested%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20former%20principal%20of%20the%20state-run%20hospital%2C%20and%20three%20others%20for%20alleged%20financial%20irregularities%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CBI%20official%20has%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20about%20some%20of%20the%20factors%20that%20have%20proved%20to%20be%20roadblocks%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20unravel%20this%20heinous%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Crime%20Scene%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20official%20said%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20join%20several%20dots%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20evidence%20from%20the%20crime%20scene%20and%20this%20has%20affected%20the%20investigation.%20The%20central%20agency%20found%20that%20Dr%20Ghosh%20ordered%20the%20demolition%20of%20a%20restroom%20and%20a%20toilet%20near%20the%20seminar%20room%20on%20August%2010%2C%20the%20day%20after%20the%20body%20was%20found.%20The%20CBI%20official%20said%20it%20is%20suspected%20that%20key%20pieces%20of%20evidence%20were%20lost%20when%20the%20Public%20Works%20Department%20carried%20out%20demolition%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20that%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20the%20seminar%20room%20crowded%20with%20people%20soon%20after%20the%20victim's%20body%20was%20found.%20Questions%20on%20whether%20the%20crime%20scene%20was%20compromised%20were%20also%20raised%20after%20the%20mob%20violence%20in%20the%20hospital%20on%20the%20night%20of%20August%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Police%2C%20however%2C%20has%20stressed%20that%20the%20crime%20scene%20was%20intact.%20%26quot%3BA%20video%20has%20gone%20viral%20showing%20the%20place%20of%20occurrence.%20This%20is%20a%20clarification.%20The%20body%20found%20in%20the%20seminar%20hall%20was%20in%20one%20portion%20of%20the%20seminar%20hall.%2040%20feet%20of%20the%20room%20was%20cordoned%20off.%20The%20video%20is%20outside%20the%20cordoned-off%20area%20where%20family%20members%2C%20doctors%20and%20the%20police%20were%20present%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Kolkata%20Police%20spokesperson%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20after%20the%20mob%20violence%2C%20the%20cops%20had%20said%20the%20crime%20scene%20was%20intact%20and%20warned%20against%20spreading%20fake%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESanjoy%20Roy%20Only%20Accused%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20parents%20had%20said%20in%20their%20petition%20in%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20that%20they%20suspected%20gangrape.%20They%20have%20also%20alleged%20that%20evidence%20and%20the%20crime%20scene%20were%20tampered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20reached%20there%20(after%20her%20death)%2C%20we%20found%20several%20people%20inside%20the%20seminar%20hall%2C%20one%20policeman%20guarding%20the%20entrance%20of%20it%20and%20many%20more%20standing%20outside.%20It%20can%20be%20assumed%20that%20the%20entire%20scene%20was%20very%20carefully%20arranged.%20Going%20by%20the%20brutality%20of%20the%20crime%2C%20the%20scene%20could%20not%20be%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20victim's%20mother%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20official%20blamed%20lack%20of%20evidence%20for%20affecting%20the%20investigation.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20evidence%20in%20this%20case.%20That%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20our%20detectives%20are%20unable%20to%20come%20to%20a%20conclusion.%20Circumstantial%20evidence%2C%20questioning%20of%20people%20and%20the%20DNA%20evidence%20do%20not%20show%20involvement%20of%20multiple%20persons%20in%20the%20sexual%20assault%20on%20the%20woman%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20DNA%20tests%20found%20a%20match%20between%20the%20victim%20and%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeparate%20DNA%20profiling%20on%20samples%20gathered%20from%20the%20victim%20and%20Roy%20and%20the%20DNA%20comparing%20with%20other%20seized%20evidence%20from%20the%20crime%20scene%20also%20corroborated%20the%20CFSL%20report%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20lawyer%20representing%20Sanjoy%20Roy%20has%20said%20he%20had%20been%20framed%20to%20shield%20the%20actual%20criminals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinancial%20Irregularities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20into%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20has%20opened%20a%20can%20of%20worms%20and%20unearthed%20massive%20corruption%20in%20the%20hospital.%20While%20Mr%20Ghosh%20and%20three%20others%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20the%20CBI%20official%20said%20they%20have%20found%20more%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20people%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20irregularities%20which%20were%20carried%20out%20in%20a%20well-planned%20manner%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20there%20were%20no%20footprints%20of%20financial%20misconduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20agency%20has%20told%20a%20court%20Dr%20Ghosh%20played%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20siphoning%20off%20funds%20and%20was%20behind%2084%20illegal%20appointments%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20principal%20from%202022%20to%202023.%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20is%20conducting%20a%20simultaneous%20investigation%20of%20the%20alleged%20financial%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20found%20that%20the%20former%20principal%20and%20his%20wife%20own%20a%20luxurious%20bungalow%20in%20South%2024%20Parganas%20district%20and%20more%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725855600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F277sh2l8_kolkata-protest_625x300_09_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-cbi-official-lists-big-roadblocks-in-its-probe-into-kolkata-rape-murder-6522600%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20been%20a%20month%20since%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20was%20found%20raped%20and%20killed%20at%20a%20seminar%20hall%20in%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-doctor-rape-murder-rg-kar-medical-college-cbi-official-lists-big-roadblocks-in-its-probe-into-kolkata-rape-murder-6522600%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Massive%20Midnight%20Protests%20In%20Kolkata%2C%20Rape-Murder%20Case%20In%20Top%20Court%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20today%20hear%20the%20case%20related%20to%20the%20brutal%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20the%20state-run%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20August%209.%20A%20bench%20comprising%20Chief%20Justice%20DY%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20will%20oversee%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20night%2C%20thousands%20gathered%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20demanding%20justice%20for%20the%20victim.%20These%20demonstrations%20were%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20wave%20of%20protests%2C%20organised%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20%26quot%3BReclaim%20the%20Night%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20movement%20calling%20for%20safety%20and%20justice%20for%20women%20in%20public%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupreme%20Court's%20Earlier%20Hearing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20August%2020%20termed%20the%20incident%20%26quot%3Bhorrific%26quot%3B%20and%20took%20additional%20measures%20to%20address%20safety%20concerns%20within%20the%20healthcare%20sector.%20The%20court%20issued%20several%20directives%2C%20including%20the%20formation%20of%20a%2010-member%20National%20Task%20Force%20to%20develop%20protocols%20for%20ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20doctors%20and%20healthcare%20workers%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20called%20upon%20protesting%20doctors%20who%20had%20been%20striking%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20victim%20to%20return%20to%20work%2C%20stating%20that%20%26quot%3Bjustice%20and%20medicine%20cannot%20be%20stopped.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20initially%20faced%20delays%2C%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20during%20its%20hearing%20on%20August%2022%2C%20criticising%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20for%20their%20sluggish%20handling%20of%20the%20investigation.%20It%20was%20not%20until%20August%2013%20that%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20intervened%2C%20transferring%20the%20investigation%20from%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%20The%20CBI%20began%20its%20probe%20the%20following%20day%2C%20August%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20body%20was%20discovered%20in%20a%20seminar%20hall%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20on%20August%209%2C%20bearing%20severe%20injuries.%20A%20civic%20volunteer%20was%20arrested%20the%20next%20day%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20crime%2C%20but%20the%20investigation%20has%20since%20widened%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20college's%20former%20principal%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%20Worldwide%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20streets%20of%20Kolkata%20to%20the%20cities%20of%20Europe%2C%20Asia%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20the%20global%20Indian%20community%20rallied%20for%20justice%20Sunday%20night.%20Over%20130%20protests%20took%20place%20in%2025%20countries%2C%20including%20major%20cities%20like%20Stockholm%2C%20Sydney%2C%20and%20New%20York.%20Protesters%20-%20many%20clad%20in%20black%20-held%20vigils%2C%20sang%20in%20Bengali%2C%20and%20chanted%20slogans%20in%20solidarity%20with%20the%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20streets%20of%20Kolkata%20were%20transformed%20into%20protest%20sites%20as%20men%20and%20women%2C%20young%20and%20old%2C%20took%20to%20the%20streets%20to%20demand%20justice.%20From%20forming%20human%20chains%20to%20holding%20burning%20torches%2C%20protesters%20expressed%20their%20anger%20and%20sorrow%20for%20the%20victim%2C%20who%20they%20symbolically%20named%20%26quot%3BTilottama%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BAbhaya.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20think%20about%20the%20torment%2C%20the%20pain%20experienced%20by%20my%20daughter%20on%20that%20night%2C%20I%20shudder.%20She%20had%20dreams%20to%20serve%20society.%20Now%2C%20all%20these%20protesters%20are%20my%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20victim's%20mother%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2014-kilometre-long%20human%20chain%20stretching%20from%20Shyambazar%20in%20North%20Kolkata%20to%20the%20suburb%20of%20Sodepur%20was%20also%20organised.%20Thousands%20of%20citizens%2C%20including%20rival%20football%20fans%20from%20East%20Bengal%2C%20Mohun%20Bagan%2C%20and%20Mohammedan%20Sporting%2C%20stood%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%2C%20united%20in%20their%20call%20for%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECentre%20vs%20State%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20protests%2C%20a%20political%20clash%20has%20emerged%20between%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%2C%20with%20the%20former%20accusing%20the%20state%20of%20%26quot%3Bunpardonable%26quot%3B%20non-cooperation%20in%20extending%20logistical%20support%20to%20the%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%2C%20which%20was%20tasked%20with%20providing%20security%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College.%20The%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20in%20its%20application%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20has%20called%20the%20lack%20of%20cooperation%20from%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20government%20%26quot%3Bsymptomatic%20of%20a%20systemic%20malaise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20has%20urged%20the%20top%20court%20to%20direct%20the%20West%20Bengal%20government%20to%20fully%20cooperate%20with%20the%20CISF%2C%20failing%20which%20it%20has%20requested%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20the%20officials%20responsible%20for%20non-compliance%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725855360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F9oue1v9o_kolkata-protests-ani-_625x300_09_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fday-after-global-protests-kolkata-rape-murder-case-in-supreme-court-today-6522210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20today%20hear%20the%20case%20related%20to%20the%20brutal%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20the%20state-run%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20August%209.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fday-after-global-protests-kolkata-rape-murder-case-in-supreme-court-today-6522210%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rare%20coin%20hidden%20for%20decades%20by%20American%20family%20could%20fetch%20over%20%24500%2C000%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725855276000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113180350%2Cimgsize-364700.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Frare-coin-hidden-for-decades-by-american-family-could-fetch-over-500000