ted%2C%20well-read%2C%20a%20strategist%20with%20deep%20thinking%20on%20any%20subject%20and%20sometimes%20it%20is%20not%20very%20easy%20to%20understand%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pitroda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Texas%2C%20USA%3A%20Chairman%20of%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%2C%20Sam%20Pitroda%20says%2C%20%26quot%3B...Rahul%20Gandhi's%20agenda%20is%20to%20address%20some%20of%20the%20larger%20issues%2C%20he%20has%20a%20vision%20contrary%20to%20what%20BJP%20promotes%20by%20spending%20crore%20and%20crore%20of%20rupees.%20I%20must%20tell%20you%20he%20is%20not%20'Pappu'%2C%20he%20is%20highly%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F28zgNI6BQj%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F28zgNI6BQj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1832950038068351332%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EChairman%20of%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Pitroda%20said%20that%20Gandhian%20thoughts%2C%20inclusion%20and%20diversity%20were%20at%20the%20core%20of%20his%20(Pitroda's)%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoing%20to%20school%20in%20the%20early%20fifties%2C%20Gandhian%20thoughts%20were%20the%20core%20of%20our%20learning.%20Inclusion%20and%20diversity%20were%20not%20just%20words%2C%20this%20is%20what%20we%20lived%20by%2C%20and%20when%20I%20begin%20to%20see%20changes%20in%20our%20society%20that%20attack%20the%20basic%20fabric%2C%20I%20worry%20about%20it.%20So%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20respect%20our%20people%20irrespective%20of%20their%20race%2C%20religion%2C%20language%2C%20or%20state.%20We%20create%20the%20same%20opportunities%20for%20everybody%20we%20provide%20dignity%20to%20labour%20and%20these%20are%20the%20issues%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20championing%20and%20that%20makes%20me%20very%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%20said%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20agenda%20is%20to%20celebrate%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi%20has%20a%20different%20agenda%20which%20is%20more%20focused%20on%20something%20that%20we%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20address%20for%20a%20long%20time%20but%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20quite%20address%20well%20and%20that%20is%20inclusion%2C%20celebration%20of%20diversity..%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%20explained%20that%20democracy%20is%20not%20that%20simple%20and%20cannot%20be%20taken%20for%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDemocracy%20is%20not%20that%20simple...%20Democracy%20requires%20work%20from%20a%20large%20number%20of%20people%20like%20us.%20We%20can't%20take%20it%20for%20granted%20because%20there%20are%20people%20who%20are%20focused%20on%20hijacking%20democracy.%20We%20have%20seen%20it%20in%20many%20countries...%20At%20the%20time%20of%20independence%2C%20there%20was%20this%20fervor%20about%20the%20independence%20movement%20and%20leaders%20like%20Gandhi%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Maulana%20Azad%2C%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%20and%20Subhash%20Chandra%20Bose%20were%20very%20clear%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20nation%20they%20wanted%20to%20build.%20Everyone%20understood%20what%20freedom%20meant%20and%20the%20opportunities%20free%20India%20would%20create...%20I%20want%20you%20to%20join%20the%20Indian%20Overseas%20Congress%2C%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20activities%2C%20and%20the%20quantity%20of%20our%20members%2C%20and%20bring%20in%20a%20more%20diverse%20group%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20was%20here%20last%20time%20visiting%20us%20at%20a%20major%20meeting%20in%20New%20York%2C%20there%20was%20a%20demand%20for%20him%20to%20come%20to%20Dallas%20and%20he%20promised%20them%20that%20during%20my%20next%20trip%2C%20I%20will%20come%20to%20Dallas%20and%20he%20is%20keeping%20his%20promise.%20He%20walks%20the%20talk%20and%20I%20am%20delighted%20that%20from%20his%20busy%20schedule%2C%20he%20could%20take%20three%20days%20off%20to%20come%20visit%20us%20where%20he%20is%20spending%20a%20day%20here%20and%20two%20days%20in%20Washington%20DC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20IOC%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndian%20Overseas%20Congress%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20looking%20after%20all%20of%20the%20global%20party%20initiatives.%20We%20are%20in%2032%20countries%20and%20our%20job%20is%20to%20get%20people%20to%20understand%20what%20our%20party%20stands%20for%2C%20and%20what%20we%20believe%20in%2C%20and%20align%20forces%20of%20all%20kinds%20of%20democratic%20initiatives.%20We%20have%20been%20at%20this%20for%20a%20while%20now%20we%20are%20in%2032%20countries%20and%20our%20job%20is%20to%20increase%20our%20membership%2C%20improve%20our%20events%20and%20activities%2C%20and%20get%20more%20people%20working%20towards%20protecting%20our%20democracy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725855240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fopd664gg_rahul-gandhi-sam-pitroda_625x300_09_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwith-rahul-gandhi-on-dais-congress-sam-pitroda-says-he-is-no-pappu-6522559%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Sam%20Pitroda%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20Indian%20diaspora%20in%20Texas%2C%20said%20that%20his%20party%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20a%20vision%20contrary%20to%20what%20BJP%20promotes%20and%20that%20he%20is%20not%20a%20%26quot%3BPappu%26quot%3B.