20Lazarus%20Beach%2C%20which%20was%20only%20a%20three-minute%20walk%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263fce095-b274-48c6-93ea-4f8ef659b294%5C%22%3EAlthough%20it%20was%20a%20weekday%2C%20all%20five%20homes%20were%20booked%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224527%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20women%20walk%20their%20dog%20at%20Lazarus%20Island%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d0199c43b5e59d16b654a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223115%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAll%20five%20tiny%20homes%20were%20booked%20when%20the%20author%20visited%20on%20a%20weekday.%20%3Cp%3EErin%20Liam%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20walking%20to%20the%20beach%2C%20I%20met%20other%20guests%20%E2%80%94%20a%20couple%20with%20their%20cavalier%20and%20their%20friend%2C%20who%20brought%20her%20cocker%20spaniel.%20The%20group%20had%20booked%20two%20homes%20to%20celebrate%20the%20cavalier's%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cocker%20spaniel's%20owner%2C%20who%20is%20in%20her%2030s%20and%20works%20in%20banking%2C%20said%20the%20accommodation%20was%20spacious%20enough%20for%20her%20and%20her%20dog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concept%20of%20this%20place%20is%20to%20unplug%20from%20busy%20life%20and%20be%20close%20to%20nature.%20It's%20a%20good%20message.%20The%20way%20the%20unit%20is%20placed%2C%20you%20can%20constantly%20be%20looking%20out%20at%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20although%20every%20room%20has%20a%20TV%20with%20a%20Netflix%20subscription%2C%20she%20tried%20not%20to%20watch%20it.%20Instead%2C%20she%20brought%20a%20book.%20%26quot%3BI'll%20try%20not%20to%20think%20about%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20from%20my%20home%2C%20there%20was%20a%20family%20with%20two%20young%20boys.%20While%20swatting%20mosquitoes%20away%2C%20the%20father%2C%20a%20doctor%20in%20his%20late%2030s%2C%20told%20me%20he%20had%20learned%20about%20the%20accommodation%20through%20local%20media.%20As%20the%20place%20was%20popular%2C%20he%20had%20to%20book%20it%20months%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20enjoyed%20the%20island's%20peacefulness%20and%20said%20the%20beach%20was%20kid-friendly%2C%20with%20gentle%20waves%20and%20fine%20sand.%20Still%2C%20he%20felt%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilt-tiny-house-parents-backyard-rent-free-saved-money-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etiny%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20too%20small%20for%20his%20family%20of%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3EI'll%20definitely%20be%20back%20again%20with%20my%20wife%2C%20hopefully%20when%20our%20parents%20can%20take%20care%20of%20the%20kids%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22980fead2-07e2-4d39-8298-745428d83661%5C%22%3EWord%20to%20the%20wise%3A%20There%20are%20very%20limited%20food%20options%20on%20the%20island%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20island%20has%20a%20convenience%20store%2C%20but%20it's%20closed%20on%20weekdays.%20Guests%20can%20preorder%20ready-to-eat%20microwave%20meals%20for%20%246%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20selected%20%E2%80%94%20or%20bring%20their%20own%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20night%20fell%2C%20my%20food%20had%20not%20arrived.%20After%20contacting%20customer%20service%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20the%20staff%20had%20forgotten%20about%20my%20meal%20and%20had%20headed%20back%20to%20the%20mainland%20at%206%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20each%20room%20was%20stocked%20with%20snacks%20and%20instant%20noodles.%20As%20I%20poured%20hot%20water%20into%20my%20chicken-flavored%20cup%20noodles%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20world%20away%20from%20being%20on%20the%20mainland%2C%20where%20you%20can%20find%20food%20options%20at%20any%20hour%20and%20have%20them%20delivered%20within%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22274f9391-d1aa-4541-950a-0162c91e87c0%5C%22%3EI%20woke%20up%20to%20the%20clucks%20of%20a%20common%20house%20gecko%20and%20birds%20chirping%20in%20the%20distanc